    "created_at": "2016-05-06T11:26:18Z",
    "updated_at": "2016-05-06T11:26:18Z",
    "body": "After looking into it I'm afraid this is a platform limitation on Windows and Linux, so on those platforms the system would \"lock\" the app into focused state when it is in the alwaysOnTop state, and the blur event will never emit. So I'm closing this as won't fix.\n"
